                <h5>1. Does Alaska Airlines offer a 24-hour cancellation policy? </h5>
                <p class="text-justify">Yes, Alaska Airlines offers a 24-hour risk-free cancellation policy. According to this policy, you get to cancel your reservation within 24 hours of booking. You do not need to pay any cancellation fees, irrespective of your chosen fare type. </p>

